social_posts.post_text: The best BBQ side on the planet! Our creamy, delicious Mac & Cheese! 🧀🔥 #BARKBARBECUE #NYC #TimeOutMarketNewYork #Dumbo #Brooklyn #NYC
#SundayFunday calls for our WOLF ATTACK Smokin’ Tater Tots! 🍟🐺 Topped with melted cheddar, onions, jalapeños, and our signature Wolf Ketchup! #WOLFNIGHTS #NYC

MOZZARELLA PARADISE at Lena’s Italian Kitchen (@lenasitaliankitchen) in NYC! Locations in Kips Bay & the Upper East Side. This place is a pickup or delivery spot only. We absolutely loved it and they did not pay us to post this. We paid full price. 🤤🍝🔥 #DEVOURPOWER
The PULLED BEEF LOADED FRIES from @khokhaeats in Piscataway, New Jersey! 🍟🤤 Oh my GOD, these are so good. Today was a great day. 👌 Can’t wait to show you what else we devoured! #DEVOURPOWER
VODKA MEATBALL BURRATA SUB from @elmstreetdiner in Stamford, CT! 🔥 This place is a devouring paradise. 🤤 #DEVOURPOWER #asmr
Williamsburg BK… Did you know you can add ANY CHEESE to your Dutch Crunch Roll when ordering our house-made Tomato Soup? 🍞🧀🔥 #MISSIONSANDWICH #Brooklyn #NYC

Just a quick video to let you know that the CHEESY, “DUTCH CRUNCH" BREAD & TOMATO SOUP from @missionsandwich in Williamsburg, Brooklyn NYC is 🔥🔥! How can this spot get any better? 🤤 DEVOURPOWER #CheesyBread #NYC

social_posts.post_text: The MOZZARELLA STICK SAMPLER from @tonyboloneys in New Jersey! 🧀💥 We had such a fun & DEVOUR-worthy visit. Which one are you trying first? Available at all of their locations. #DEVOURPOWER #MozzarellaSticks #NJ
VODKA PARM BURRATA MEATBALL SUB from @elmstreetdiner in Stamford, CT! 🤤 Treat yourself this weekend, DEVOURERS. You deserve it. 👊 #DEVOURPOWER #MeatballSub #Burrata #CT
The CHICKEN TIKKA MAC & CHEESE (with extra fried chicken) from @eat.namkeen in Williamsburg, Brooklyn NYC! 🧀🍗🔥 We freakin’ love this spot. 👌 #DEVOURPOWER #FriedChicken #MacnCheese #NYC
The SAMPLER MAC from Sarita’s Mac & Cheese (S’MAC) in NYC’s East Village! 🧀🧀🧀 8 different kinds of mac in one freakin order! Which flavor would you DEVOUR first? #DEVOURPOWER
Still dreaming of the MOZZARELLA SAMPLER from @tonyboloneys in Hoboken, NJ! 🧀💥 Which mozzarella stick are you DEVOURING first? 🤤 #DEVOURPOWER #MozzarellaSticks #NJ

This Open Face Sandwich Joint, @filthyflats, in Brooklyn, NY serves up some DEVOUR-worthy items… like this BUFFALO CHICKEN FLAT loaded with melted mozzarella cheese, buffalo sauce, and blue cheese dressing. 🍗🔥 Count us in, every time. 🤤 #DEVOURPOWER
The PECORINO ROMANO CHEESE WHEEL PASTA with CHICKEN CUTLET from @roccosofrocbeach in Queens, NYC! 🍝🧀🍗😍 How could we ever say no to this? 🤤 #DEVOURPOWER #PASTA #CHEESEWHEEL #NYC
The cheesiest and most DEVOUR-worthy BAKED ZITI I’ve ever had is coming out of @roccosofrocbeach in Queens, NYC! 🍝🤤 Keep it cheesy, friends. 🧀 #DEVOURPOWER
The DOUBLE SAUSAGE PARM HERO from @marinarapizzanyc in NYC’s Upper West Side (97th & Broadway)! 🥖🔥🤤 Cheesy, meaty, and just downright DEVOUR-worthy. 💪 #DEVOURPOWER
The JERK CHICKEN MAC & CHEESE from @halalbrosgrill in Brooklyn, NYC! 🍗🔥🧀🤤 We can’t get enough of this spot. Who’s hungry? #DEVOURPOWER
The FOCACCIA TUNA MELT from our friends at @marksoffmadison ALWAYS hits the spot. 🥖💥🤤 Cheesy, packed with tuna salad, and a perfect crunch. 👌 #DEVOURPOWER
The RICOTTA SCRAMBLE TOAST from @eggshopnyc in Williamsburg, Brooklyn is one of our faves. 🍳🥖🔥 #DEVOURPOWER
The FRIED CHEESE APPETIZERS for the WIN from @streettotable in Merrick, NY! 🧀🔥🤤 LOVE this spot. Which are you DEVOURING? #DEVOURPOWER
I could watch (and DEVOUR) the giant TRADTIONAL LASAGNA get made from @roccosofrocbeach in Queens NYC all day long. 🍝🤯🤤 Who’s hungry?! #DEVOURPOWER
LAMB NIHARI BUTTER CHICKEN SAUCE MAC & CHEESE from @mumbaidreamsnyack in Nyack, NY! 🧀🤯🤤 Indian fusion, in the best way possible. #DEVOURPOWER
The NASHVILLE HOT CHICKEN MAC & CHEESE from @fluffieshotchicken in New Jersey NEEDS to be on your list! 🍗🧀🔥🤤 Locations in Bayonne and Hackensack. #DEVOURPOWER
The PEPPERONI & CHEESE STUFFED CRUST VODKA SICILIAN PIZZA from @MarinaraPizzaNYC! 🧀🍕🤤 Available only at their Upper West Side location on Broadway in NYC! #DEVOURPOWER #NeverTooMuchCheese
CHEESY JERK CHICKEN GYRO for the win, always, at @halalbrosgrill in Brooklyn, NYC! 🍗🧀🫓🔥 Lunch is served, devourers. #DEVOURPOWER #NYC #HALAL
The OVEN BAKED MAC & CHEESE from @grottobk in Bedstuy, Brooklyn NYC is a MUST. 🧀🤤 Who’s hungry? #DEVOURPOWER
